{"tid":1847563,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet 回歸超過一個月　〈Psycho〉持續征服音樂節目！","createTime":"2020-01-28T06:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T06:14:01.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b671c87477b0a06dd24ba7d18b0149ae7c6634","tid":1847563,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T06:04:34.000Z","msg":"Red Velvet 毫無宣傳的&rdquo;Psycho&rdquo; 人氣卻居高不下，一轉眼十冠王頭銜也已近在眼前！<br />\n<br />\nKBS 2TV 的《Music Bank》昨天（27 日）在官方網站上公開 1 月第四週的 K-Chart 排名，結果顯示 Red Velvet 以 &ldquo;Psycho&rdquo; 擊敗 Zico 和 IU 而拿下冠軍。<br />\n<br />\nRed Velvet 這次發片後的第一座音樂節目獎盃，便是於 1 月 3 日在 《Music Bank》拿下的；之後她們接連橫掃 MBC、SBS 各大無線台的音樂節目，目前為止已經累積九座冠軍獎盃了。<br />\n<br />\n究竟這次 Red Velvet 能否繼 &ldquo;Power Up&rdquo; 後再創十冠王紀錄？就讓我們拭目以待啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/123810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F123810&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=83a1f296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/123810</a>"},{"pid":"3979cf69ede5c3d4f377ed397c6df3ebaab072e0","tid":1847563,"uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T06:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/cbefa7e18eb7e7d53f3ff22d6dee936b/ec90f1d748badfa2-fe/s400x600/d5f6ac42ddfce462df093c214a97ef89cff61bd4.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fcbefa7e18eb7e7d53f3ff22d6dee936b%2Fec90f1d748badfa2-fe%2Fs400x600%2Fd5f6ac42ddfce462df093c214a97ef89cff61bd4.gifv&h=927c6c97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/aea88124d650357e6879fee328b2c890/ec90f1d748badfa2-52/s400x600/f6c6e7ef6afc7cd8d5632733c2413acf335010e0.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Faea88124d650357e6879fee328b2c890%2Fec90f1d748badfa2-52%2Fs400x600%2Ff6c6e7ef6afc7cd8d5632733c2413acf335010e0.gifv&h=2496e77c&